name: Zentry
description: Zentry is building the Human-Agentic Operating System—a next-gen AI + crypto infrastructure where human life fuels AI, and AI in turn amplifies human potential. Through its tri-layer stack (zApp, zAI, zData), Zentry transforms everyday activity into structured data, trains intelligent agents, and powers a new user-owned economy. It's not just tech—it’s a platform for civilization-scale co-evolution between people and machines.
